posting_body: ['For leasing info call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#187394', 'This community offers sophisticated interiors with stunning finishes and plenty of desirable upgrades.', 'Surround yourself with luxurious amenities such as a state-of-the-art fitness center, an infinity edge pool and a full-service spa with an on-site massage therapist.', 'Experience an ultra luxe outdoor environment with landscaped courtyards, outdoor kitchens, private cabanas, and a spacious dog park for your furry friend.', 'Our location sits in the heart of both the Houston Medical Center and Rice University, and offers direct access to Buffalo Bayou running trails.', 'We also have quick access to Loop 610, Highway 59, and Highway 288 to enjoy events at nearby venues.', 'When you combine the ultimate location, luxury outdoor living, and sophisticated, upgraded floor plans, you’ve found your next home.', 'You’ll love coming home to this center where sophistication meets an active lifestyle.', 'In your spacious apartment, quartz countertops and wood flooring offer an elegant escape from a long day.', 'Share a glass of wine with friends in your gourmet kitchen, break a sweat in our state-of-the-art fitness center, or take a dip in our infinity edge pool.', 'With other stylish amenities like Whirlpool stainless steel appliances and iconic views, this apartment offers a unique living experience in Houston’s Medical Center.', 'Community Amenities', '24/7 Package Lockers', 'Business Center', 'Clubhouse', 'Community Conference Center', 'Cyber Library', 'Demonstration Kitchen', 'Dog Park', 'Dog Washing Station', 'EV Charging Stations', 'Fitness Center', 'Game Room', 'Parking Garage', 'Picnic Area', 'Stainless Steel BBQ Grilling Area/Outdoor Kitchen', 'Swimming Pool & Cabanas']
